if you didn't do anything.

14:15.332 --> 14:16.812
Get on your knees.

14:16.856 --> 14:18.031
Get up. Come on.

14:18.074 --> 14:19.771
Go.

14:20.772 --> 14:22.687
It's not my gun.

14:22.731 --> 14:23.950
It was in your pants.

14:23.993 --> 14:25.429
Yeah, 'cause I was
holding it for someone.

14:25.473 --> 14:26.126
Who?

14:27.170 --> 14:28.476
I can't say.

14:28.519 --> 14:30.391
