in five different homicides.

14:38.878 --> 14:40.270
Do you understand
what that means?

14:40.314 --> 14:41.445
It means this gun

14:41.489 --> 14:43.099
was used to kill five people.

14:43.143 --> 14:44.971
And the gun was found
on your person,

14:45.014 --> 14:47.451
which means you killed
the five people.

14:47.495 --> 14:50.890
It ain't me, man.
I didn't kill nobody.

14:50.933 --> 14:52.674
You really think
a jury's gonna believe that?

14:52.717 --> 14:54.284
Ladies and gentlemen
of the jury,

14:54.328 --> 14:55.633
the ballistics on this weapon

14:55.677 --> 14:58.158
match the evidence
found in multiple homicides.

14:58.201 --> 15:00.943
The defendant's fingerprints
were found on the weapon,

15:00.987 --> 15:02.597
and the detective in the case

15:02.640 --> 15:05.687
found the weapon
on the defendant.

15:06.993 --> 15:09.821
Doesn't take a rocket scientist
to figure out who the killer is.

15:09.865 --> 15:11.301
Well, it ain't me,
'cause I didn't kill nobody.

15:11.345 --> 15:13.956
Well, somebody did,
and my money is on you.

15:14.000 --> 15:15.610
Man, I did not kill anybody.

15:15.653 --> 15:17.394
Then who did?I don't know!

15:17.438 --> 15:20.180
All you have to do
is give us a name.

15:21.833 --> 15:23.792
I can't.

15:23.835 --> 15:25.576
You can't, or you won't?

15:25.620 --> 15:27.578
Are you scared?
You think if you talk to us,

15:27.622 --> 15:28.753
you're gonna get whacked?

15:30.799 --> 15:33.933
I'm not scared of nothing, miss.
I just can't.

15:38.024 --> 15:40.678
So, what are you gonna say?Honestly, I have no idea.

15:40.722 --> 15:42.767
No planYeah, I know.

15:42.811 --> 15:45.640
Does she have any
idea what's coming?Not a clue.

15:47.598 --> 15:49.818
Here she comes.Wait, where are you going?

15:49.861 --> 15:51.515
Far, far away.

15:51.559 --> 15:54.431
Hey, Nicky.Anthony.

15:54.475 --> 15:56.216
Twice in the same week.

15:56.259 --> 15:58.740
You must really miss me.Always.

15:58.783 --> 16:00.394
That's not why I'm here.

16:01.438 --> 16:03.005
Why don't we take a seat?

16:03.049 --> 16:06.487
I'm here because of Nicky.
You think he's too old for me.

16:06.530 --> 16:08.619
That is not it.

16:08.663 --> 16:10.621
I like that he's
more mature.

16:10.665 --> 16:12.841
