just running around

16:12.884 --> 16:13.885
like drunken frat boys.

16:13.929 --> 16:16.453
I like being with a man.

16:16.497 --> 16:18.194
It's true.

16:18.238 --> 16:20.936
He's a man and I'm a woman.

16:20.980 --> 16:23.373
That's something
that I hope you can accept.

16:23.417 --> 16:25.027
But you're still a young woman,

16:25.071 --> 16:27.551
one with not a lot
of experience.

16:27.595 --> 16:29.858
Um, Mom, I hate to
break it to you,

16:29.901 --> 16:32.730
but I have a lot more
experience than you think.

16:33.775 --> 16:36.169
I was not talking sexually,

16:36.212 --> 16:37.518
but thank you for that.

16:37.561 --> 16:39.955
I was talking
about life experiences,

16:39.999 --> 16:43.741
talking about seeing things
as they really are

16:43.785 --> 16:45.874
and not as they appear to be.

16:45.917 --> 16:47.223
What are you getting at?

16:48.268 --> 16:52.359
Your new boyfriend's uncle
is Ray Giannopoulos.

16:52.402 --> 16:56.928
His sister, Nicholas's mother,
is Sofia Papadopoulos.

16:56.972 --> 16:58.930
Okay, and?

16:58.974 --> 17:02.717
