tells me that...

17:36.055 --> 17:38.231
...there is a connection
between him dating you

17:38.274 --> 17:39.928
and me investigating his uncle.

17:39.971 --> 17:41.277
Of course you think that,
because you think

17:41.321 --> 17:42.800
everything is about you.

17:42.844 --> 17:44.019
Nicky.Why can't you

17:44.063 --> 17:46.282
just be happy that I'm happy?

17:54.334 --> 17:56.118
Everything okay?

17:56.162 --> 17:57.641
Yeah.

17:57.685 --> 18:00.122
I saw your car outside.

18:00.166 --> 18:01.384
Oh, I just came by to check in.

18:05.432 --> 18:07.303
Check in about what?

18:07.347 --> 18:09.262
Got something on my mind

18:09.305 --> 18:10.959
I wanted to talk
to you about.

18:11.002 --> 18:14.963
But I just realized I came here
not as your son but as a cop.

18:15.006 --> 18:17.139
As a sergeant, actually,

18:17.183 --> 18:19.794
who has an opinion
on what we did today

18:19.837 --> 18:22.666
at the Beame Complex
in your precinct.

18:22.710 --> 18:25.016
Thanks for this.

18:26.017 --> 18:28.542
That's right.

18:28.585 --> 18:30.718
You're not the only one

18:30.761 --> 18:33.634
