18:41.903 --> 18:44.862
would just be
like a slap on the wrist

18:44.906 --> 18:47.822
in return for a punch
in the face.

18:47.865 --> 18:49.824
What are we gonna do,
call 'em names?

18:49.867 --> 18:53.219
But this shock and awe, Dad.

18:53.262 --> 18:56.091
Seems like one step
forward, two steps back

18:56.135 --> 18:58.920
