the perfect decision

19:24.119 --> 19:27.253
means you'll never make
any decision.

19:28.819 --> 19:30.778
I get that.

19:31.822 --> 19:33.302
The hard part

19:33.346 --> 19:36.479
is finding a way
to live with yourself

19:36.523 --> 19:38.873
if you made the wrong one.

19:45.967 --> 19:48.448
REPORTER: It was quite the scene
