We need to talk.

20:11.993 --> 20:13.777
I'm a little busy right now.

20:13.821 --> 20:15.344
Frank, it's important.

20:15.388 --> 20:17.128
How important?I just watched

20:17.172 --> 20:20.567
a man compare the NYPD
to an occupying army,

20:20.610 --> 20:22.873
