the city of New York.

22:11.025 --> 22:14.202
I need your support.With what?

22:14.245 --> 22:16.030
He means
with the commissioner.

22:16.073 --> 22:17.814
The commissioner?

22:17.858 --> 22:20.469
So formal
this afternoon, Abigail.

22:20.513 --> 22:21.775
It feels appropriate
to the circumstances.

22:21.818 --> 22:23.124
And what are the circumstances?

22:23.167 --> 22:24.430
You called the meeting.

22:24.473 --> 22:26.432
Apparently
to talk about our boss

22:26.475 --> 22:28.738
behind closed doors,
behind his back.

22:28.782 --> 22:30.131
Hey.
I'm just telling
it like it is.

22:30.174 --> 22:30.958
Just what kind
of support

22:31.001 --> 22:32.089
you looking for, Garrett?

