23:41.942 --> 23:42.812
What kind of situation?

23:42.856 --> 23:43.857
Is he in trouble?

23:43.900 --> 23:44.597
What's up with Jack?

23:44.640 --> 23:46.163
Nothing.

23:46.207 --> 23:48.688
