how strict Dad was with us.

24:39.042 --> 24:40.827
Excuse me?DANNY:
He wasn't even strict with him.

24:40.870 --> 24:42.524
He was too worn out
from being strict

24:42.568 --> 24:43.917
with me, you, and Joe
all the time.

24:43.960 --> 24:46.615
I don't think I was that strict
with any of you.

24:46.659 --> 24:48.487
I would have

