me cut it in half.

24:51.881 --> 24:53.579
That was half?

24:53.622 --> 24:55.842
I don't even want to know about
the half that was left out.

24:55.885 --> 24:58.235
You want to talk about strict,
that one wrote the book.

24:58.932 --> 25:02.022
Spare the rod, spoil the child.

25:02.065 --> 25:04.024
I say good for you.

25:04.067 --> 25:05.199
Thank you.

25:05.242 --> 25:07.331
