if you want.

26:28.456 --> 26:30.458
Ready or not,
here I come.

26:34.462 --> 26:37.508
Oh. You're really beautiful.

26:37.552 --> 26:39.293
You are really charming.

26:39.336 --> 26:41.121
I love the way
you look at me.

26:41.164 --> 26:43.427
I want a picture
of that look.

26:48.650 --> 26:49.825
Something the matter?

26:49.869 --> 26:53.437
I just hate it
when my mother is right.

26:53.481 --> 26:55.178
Right about what?

26:57.093 --> 26:59.356
You.

27:02.882 --> 27:05.406
JAMIE:
Yes. No, I don't have
an estimate.

27:05.449 --> 27:07.060
Sergeant, you getting
a handle on this?

